dct_title_s: Plan de la ville et des ports de Rhodes
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by hachures. In upper margin: Pl. 60. Plate 60 from: Voyage pittoresque de la Grèce. Tome premier. A Paris, 1782. Original plate also includes: Vue du port des bateaux à Rhodes.
